org.apache.flink.graph

接口 GraphAnalytic<K,VV,EV,T>

  • 类型参数:
    K - key type
    VV - vertex value type
    EV - edge value type
    T - the return type
    所有已知实现类:
    AbstractGraphAnalytic, ChecksumHashCode, GlobalClusteringCoefficient, GlobalClusteringCoefficient, TriangleCount, TriangleCount, VertexMetrics, VertexMetrics

    public interface GraphAnalytic<K,VV,EV,T>
    A GraphAnalytic is similar to a GraphAlgorithm but is terminal and results are retrieved via accumulators. A Flink program has a single point of execution. A GraphAnalytic defers execution to the user to allow composing multiple analytics and algorithms into a single program.
